The following status flags from ROGUE will be implemented differently in DUNGEONEER:

WAKENS, WANDERS, FLITS, CAN_FLIT, SEEKS_GOLD, STATIONARY
  These are behavioral flags that will be defined in the Creature class.

RUSTS, HOLDS, FREEZES, STEALS_GOLD, STEALS_ITEM, STINGS, DRAINS_LIFE,
DROPS_LEVEL, CONFUSES, FLAMES
  Defined as a flag on weapons.  Creatures will get natural weapons with these
  characteristics.


